name: Enter Horizon
description:
Unfolding for a life-age, our hearts beyond the event horizon.

Process: A Sony KV-13FM12, Sony HVC-2400, Sony XV-5000, Panasonic WJ-MX50A, Panasonic WJ-MX30, Videonics MX-1 and Videonics VE-1A dreaming of each other, through each other. Direct capture played back through a Sony KV-13FM12 and rescanned via Nikon D7100 donning an Asahi SMC Takumar 1.8/55.
